NAME OF SERVICE : DEPARTMENT-SERVICE
PORT NUMBER     : 6002


THEY ARE FOLLOWING ENDS POINT OF DEPARTMENT
---------------------------------------------

1.

METHOD NAME: POST

URL        : http://localhost:6002/department/save

PURPOSE    : To store the department details

